_sText:
Made a few changes from v1. Removed bad textures and added new ground textures.
I've had a request to make this into an aim/awp map with access to the rooftops for sniping which
i'm going to start working on once I know this map is stable for gameplay with real players.  

Special thanks to Slayer for beta testing and locating pink textures. 

I hope this version is good.
